snippet: Prime Minister Najib Razak is not among those accused of wrongdoing in an investigation about of corruption involving the 1Malaysia Development Berhad sovereign fund.
abstract: Swiss Attorney General’s office says Malaysian Prime Min Najib Razak is not among those accused of wrongdoing in 1Malaysia Development Berhad sovereign fund.
